<i>Why be all serious now?</i>

627
00:42:26,040 --> 00:42:29,548
<i>No authority scares us</i>

628
00:42:29,748 --> 00:42:34,081
<i>What's there to fear?</i>

629
00:42:36,582 --> 00:42:38,373
And the man of the match, Madan Lal.

630
00:42:38,498 --> 00:42:43,276
<i>India wins rather comfortably,
with 5 wickets and 23 overs to spare.</i>

631
00:42:43,457 --> 00:42:47,250
<i>With two back-to-back wins,
India now on top of Group B.</i>

